title: The Kingdom
description:
The complete digital collection of The Kingdom, sequel to Kingdom Come.

While Mark Waid and Alex Ross first series explored the clash of generations and genres of the comic book medium, this followup explores how they reconcile.

After many years, the concept of the multiverse is recognised in this series and validates all the realities and stories of prior DC Universes. In a sense, I feel this is a better solution than wiping out everything in favour of Wildstormy New52, which is not to say there's some good stories happening there.

Credit to Okcomputo - Novus for the initial up of The Kingdom 01 - 02.
